# Blind SQL Injection

Blind SQL injection technique using boolean-based and time-based inference.

## Description

This technique exploits SQL injection vulnerabilities where the application
does not return query results directly but reveals information through
boolean conditions or time delays.

## Payloads

- `' OR 1=1--`
- `' OR SLEEP(5)--`
- `' AND SUBSTRING(@@version,1,1)='5'--`

## Detection

Monitor response time differences and boolean condition changes in output.
